 114:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/runtime/efirtlib.c **** Routine Description:
 115:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/runtime/efirtlib.c **** 
 116:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/runtime/efirtlib.c ****     Compares to GUIDs
